      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 quasi-static loading condition. A second loading rate or alternative boundary condition was not evaluated. Achieved level falls below the required level; this shortfall is documented and accepted given the established ASTM standardization of the F1717 protocol."
