    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-vv40-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment for COU1 is Accepted. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 is a standardized regulatory protocol with a single prescribed loading condition; multi-condition testing is not feasible within the standard framework. The Output comparison factor was reviewed qualitatively and found adequate. The model is judged sufficiently credible for its intended use in supporting a 510(k) submission.",
